column5: My buddy had a great day out there today.  Managed this nice buck with a nice rack.  11 pointer  8" base. Shot with a compound bow at 30 yards. Just to get an idea or the size of this rack, my buddy is 6'3 and weighs 250.
Wow, trophy forsure....Congrats to your friend.  TDunn
That doesn't even look like a white tail... geez it's huge
That is one old buck.Man look at the base mass. Nice shooting.
That sure is a beautiful deer, congrats to your buddy.
damb.  That doesn't look like a simcoe county deer.  Wher'd he get that brute.
With a big head like that , must've been close to 300lbs for sure.
Awesome rack. Gonna get a whole lot of peperettes from that bad boy.
Awesome Chris   :worthy: Congrats to your buddy on his harvest  Trophy buck!!! Love it Jacques
wow thats a heavy looking ol boy! congrats to your friend.  jason
I dunno simcoe and dufferin county have some pretty big brutes!
WOW !!!!!! Gongrat's nice Buck look's well fed for sure. Hangum high for 2 weeks if you can.
That is a brute. Congrats to your bud
Awesome animal, congrats to your buddy.
